main event: An observation of a high flying, reddish, glowing object was reported on July 7, 1965 in Bohemia, Maryland.
interesting points: The object was observed for approximately 15 minutes,The report concluded that the data was insufficient for evaluation,The source of the report was civilian,The document is part of Project Blue Book, which investigates UFO sightings,There are no photographs or physical evidence associated with this sighting.
